		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>Thanks Ryoku! I was able to find one installation by doing<br />
find /var/www/vhosts/ -name &#8220;revslider&#8221; -print<br />
However I&#8217;m not sure this method will work across the board because that plugin has been packaged with so many themes, I figure directory name could have been changed over time.</p>
		</div>

		
		
	</article>
	<ul class="children">

	<li class="comment odd alt depth-4" id="comment-3964">
	<article >

		
		<header class="comment-header">
			<p class="comment-author">
				<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/34fe0e2717474b39fdceeb70302729fb?s=48&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/34fe0e2717474b39fdceeb70302729fb?s=96&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' loading='lazy'/><span itemprop="name">dante_hwd</span> 			</p>

