		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>As has been explained by many others, this has been patched for months both in the plugin and many leading themes. With regards to the X theme, we have included the patched version of Slider Revolution since version 1.8.1 released in April, 2014 (11 releases ago). Put simply, the past 11 versions of X have included this patched version of Slider Revolution which our customers can always download directly from their ThemeForest download page. More information for our customers can be found in our member center here: <a href="http://theme.co/x/member/forums/topic/regarding-old-verisons-of-revolution-slider/" rel="nofollow ugc">http://theme.co/x/member/forums/topic/regarding-old-verisons-of-revolution-slider/</a></p>
