The problem came from the template itself: neighborhood by envato and the way they bundled it:<br />
<a href="http://themeforest.net/item/neighborhood-responsive-multipurpose-shop-theme/5086341" rel="nofollow ugc">http://themeforest.net/item/neighborhood-responsive-multipurpose-shop-theme/5086341</a></p>
