			<p>Something tried to access my website using this url:</p>
<p>/library.php/wp-content/themes/beach_apollo/thumb.php</p>
<p>Wed Dec 31 10:06 pm (Taipei time)</p>
<p>My site is totally independent of WP. Just thought I would mention it. Not sure if it&#8217;s related. </p>
<p>Stuff happens like this often enough where some &#8216;bot&#8217; creates a WP url that my site records but won&#8217;t allow anyone/anything access to. I just lock &#8217;em out.</p>
